snippet.title: Boti: Byteland Overclocked | Bitosaurus DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Boti: Byteland Overclocked on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2161050/Boti_Byteland_Overclocked/

The ultimate clash between Dinos and Robots continues and this time it visited Byteland!

Experience the thrill of the prehistoric era with the “Bitosaurus” DLC, a free update that adds a new skin to your collection. Transform into a fearsome Bitosaurus and roar your way through the challenges of both Single Player and Co-Op modes!

Follow us to get the latest news from Byteland!
